众，发动群众，因而就能揭第一切","index":198,"publicationId":"2cb7cbc4-c90a-45c6-ab78-275f72203079","articleId":"f4d7cacaed"},{"id":"a941d3b360","type":"paragraph","text":"于第一个五年计划期间重工业品的价格透公开的和验微的犯罪分子，使他撕到处陷于","index":199,"publicationId":"2cb7cbc4-c90a-45c6-ab78-275f72203079","articleId":"f4d7cacaed"},{"id":"05e26b3ca7","type":"paragraph","text":"步降低”。革命群众的狂洋大海中，无法藏身，更无法","index":200,"publicationId":"2cb7cbc4-c90a-45c6-ab78-275f72203079","articleId":"f4d7cacaed"},{"id":"593521e613","type":"paragraph","text":"第44真倒数第8行中，“相当于一九乘陈活动。这是我们国家肃清犯罪的无比强","index":201,"publicationId":"2cb7cbc4-c90a-45c6-ab78-275f72203079","articleId":"f4d7cacaed"},{"id":"938d535ed1","type":"paragraph","text":"四九年的五倍多，应改为“相当于一九四","index":202,"publicationId":"2cb7cbc4-c90a-45c6-ab78-275f72203079","articleId":"f4d7cacaed"},{"id":"04e6dcda3e","type":"paragraph","text":"九年的十倍”。大的方量之所在","index":203,"publicationId":"2cb7cbc4-c90a-45c6-ab78-275f72203079","articleId":"f4d7cacaed"},{"id":"bf2c5673e6","type":"paragraph","text":"我们国家肃清流、盗、烟毒、赌博、04。","index":204,"publicationId":"2cb7cbc4-c90a-45c6-ab78-275f72203079","articleId":"f4d7cacaed"},{"id":"99bc6b3bf6","type":"paragraph","text":"1959年8","index":205,"publicationId":"2cb7cbc4-c90a-45c6-ab78-275f72203079","articleId":"f4d7cacaed"},{"id":"8e00c29aee","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":206,"publicationId":"2cb7cbc4-c90a-45c6-ab78-275f72203079","articleId":"f4d7cacaed"}],"page":{"id":"b294617eeb","publicationId":"2cb7cbc4-c90a-45c6-ab78-275f72203079","articleId":"f4d7cacaed","start":40,"end":46}}}},"__N_SSG":true}